 S_{j} = \sum_{n=1}^\infty 1_{X_n = j}
 s_{ij} = E[S_j | X_1 = i] = \sum_{n=1}^\infty E[1_{X_n = j} | X_1 = i]
 = \delta_{ij} + \sum_{n=2}^\infty E[1_{X_n = j} | X_1 = i] 
 = \delta_{ij} + \sum_{n=2}^\infty \sum_k P_{ik} E[1_{X_n = j} | X_1 = i,X_2=k] 
